title: Helping Others Improve EP 10.

embed.description: This is part of a series, where I try and help others go from Bronze to silver. Heck maybe even gold. Im not the one playing, Im spectating a game. If you are bronze and want some help, let me know.

body:
I Might be trying something in the near future, which is actually trying to make better/good content.
So be on the lookout for a giveaway if I can figure out how/what/when and such.
